These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, water
City: san-francisco, hannover, new-york, rome
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to hannover and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| City      | rome | san-francisco | new-york   | hannover |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, r&b, dubstep, salsa
1. the fan of salsa is between the person who's hobby is reading and the fan of r&b##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | salsa   | folk | dubstep       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, lacrosse, ice-hockey, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person eating kale##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person eating corn##2
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating corn is the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Sport   | lacrosse | ice-hockey   | volleyball | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony, rat
House: palace, craftsman, cape-cod, farmhouse
1. the craftsman house is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the palace house and the owner of the rat##2
3. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| House   | cape-cod | farmhouse | palace | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, go, whist
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
4. the person playing whist is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Game   | monopoly        | go | whist  | billiard |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving | card-games    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, pop, salsa
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, journalist, musician, photographer
1. the musician is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the fan of salsa is the musician##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is the chef##1
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of classical and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | pop           | classical | salsa  |
| Job         | chef | photographer | journalist   | musician |

