.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, house, punk
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, almond-milk, cola
1. the fan of gospel is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the fan of electronic is between the person drinking iced-tea and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | gospel | electronic | house      |
| Beverage     | almond-milk | iced-tea    | soy-milk  | cola |

