.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, davidoff, montecristo, prince
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the helicopter is the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the montecristo-smoker and the person driving the roller##2
3. the blend-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar       | blend | prince | montecristo     | davidoff   |
| Transport   | roller   | motorbike     | snowmobile | helicopter |

