.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
City: venice, hamburg, edinburgh, new-york
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, ship, van
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person driving the boat and the person traveling to venice##2
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| City         | hamburg | edinburgh | venice | new-york |
| Transport   | boat         | van       | scooter    | ship         |

