.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, trike, snowmobile
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person driving the van and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Transport    | snowmobile   | trike      | van   | jet-ski  |
| Sport   | tennis | ice-hockey | swimming | baseball |

