.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, singing, writing
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, cat, mouse
1. the owner of the cat is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the owner of the horse##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the owner of the horse is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | singing | writing | filmmaking |
| Pet   | cat          | horse     | mouse  | bird     |

