.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
City: hamburg, boston, prague, new-york
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, documentary, sports
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is between the person watching sports movies and the person traveling to hamburg##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| City           | hamburg | new-york | boston | prague     |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | documentary    | sports   | adventure |

