2. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsbellflower##2
3. the librarian is on the right of the doctor##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the librarian##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Job           | doctor | librarian | firefighter | entrepreneur |
| Flower   | bellflower   | daisy | poppy         | aconite |

