3. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking juice and the italian##2
4. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | italian | egyptian | pakistani |
| Beverage           | mirinda  | iced-tea  | tea | juice      |

