.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, emerald, red, blood-red
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, roller, ship, skateboard
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes emerald is between the person driving the bike and the person who likes red##2
4. the person who likes blood-red is the person driving the bike##1
5. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Color       | blood-red | emerald | red | pink |
| Transport   | bike    | roller  | skateboard    | ship       |

