.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese, polish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, blend, pall-mall, chaman
1. the blend-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
3. the polish is the prince-smoker##1
4. the chaman-smoker is between the american and the chinese##2
5. the chinese is the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish   | american   | australian | chinese |
| Cigar         | prince | blend | chaman     | pall-mall    |

