.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, singing, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, rugby, badminton
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing    | sudoku     | card-games | dancing |
| Sport     | snowboarding | badminton | rugby       | cycling     |

 